<div class="title">Fighting a Lifetime of Anxiety</div>
<div class="substance">Bromazepam</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Acid_Flux&Exact=1">Acid_Flux</a></div>


